Right?

00:41:36.210 --> 00:41:38.130
So.

00:41:38.130 --> 00:41:43.750
But the answer is
always just try harder.

00:41:43.750 --> 00:41:46.720
65%, 63% of white Americans
say look, you know,

00:41:46.720 --> 00:41:50.250
blacks just not trying
hard enough to get ahead.

00:41:50.250 --> 00:41:52.970
Keep blaming racial
discrimination on everything.

00:41:52.970 --> 00:41:54.830
60 percent of white
Americans say look,

00:41:54.830 --> 00:41:56.496
you got the same or
better opportunities

00:41:56.496 --> 00:41:59.500
than everybody else, you're
just not making it happen.

00:41:59.500 --> 00:42:04.220
70 percent say you're just
