products and services from,

01:09:17.560 --> 01:09:19.119
and where do these
businesses fit in

01:09:19.119 --> 01:09:21.790
into that because those
businesses are employing people

01:09:21.790 --> 01:09:23.950
who are generate
income for families,

01:09:23.950 --> 01:09:26.162
