01:09:30.745 --> 01:09:32.979
If you have a certain
kind of economic profile,

01:09:32.979 --> 01:09:36.140
you get to move if you
don't like what's going on.

01:09:36.140 --> 01:09:37.910
You're not stuck in that spot.

01:09:37.910 --> 01:09:42.240
But if you don't, you're stuck,
you're just along for the ride.

01:09:42.240 --> 01:09:46.090
So it isn't to be to
be more specific, there

01:09:46.090 --> 01:09:50.470
are important things that we
can do with our resources.

01:09:50.470 --> 01:09:53.057
People will open up a
$500,000 bank accounts,

01:09:53.057 --> 01:09:53.890
so things like that.

01:09:53.890 --> 01:09:58.360
We got over $100
billion in a bank.

01:09:58.360 --> 01:10:01.136
Black banks only have
4.9 ish billion that kind

01:10:01.136 --> 01:10:02.260
of the last time I checked.

01:10:02.260 --> 01:10:05.170
I mean, we could
oversubscribe them in no time.

01:10:05.170 --> 01:10:07.185
If you move that money
into those banks,

01:10:07.185 --> 01:10:09.810
they'd have a hire 31,000 people
