01:10:09.810 --> 01:10:13.510
And It would generate another
$70,000 in the supply chain

01:10:13.510 --> 01:10:14.510
to be able to help that.

01:10:14.510 --> 01:10:15.561
That would be $100,000.

01:10:15.561 --> 01:10:16.060
Just that.

01:10:16.060 --> 01:10:18.310
That's before we even get
to all the lending and stuff

01:10:18.310 --> 01:10:19.727
that they would be doing.

01:10:19.727 --> 01:10:21.310
We have a lot of
stuff in our control,

01:10:21.310 --> 01:10:25.458
we just need to
do a little more.

01:10:25.458 --> 01:10:26.310
Yes sir.

